description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=1/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Compete with everyone to get the worms, but cooperate to protect the radio.  Fish Listening to Radio features a state-of-the-art ukulele sound track and super keen worm eating action.  Color the pond as you rack up points and show the other players who's king fish.
